{"tid":2045430,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國務院擬定2020/22人民幣取代港幣","createTime":"2020-05-31T21:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T09:28:55.000Z","uid":279401,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"10283c4fe0ea2444cbab8a675c647c0526dae5a3","tid":2045430,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T21:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLSxCeR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLSxCeR.jpg&h=37506fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳細分析內容：<br />\n<a href=\"http://politicalgirlriot.blogspot.com/2017/03/blog-post_28.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpoliticalgirlriot.blogspot.com%2F2017%2F03%2Fblog-post_28.html%3Fm%3D1&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=241149fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://politicalgirlriot.blogspot.com/2017/03/blog-post_28.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n國安法咁急於立法，為左取代港幣舖路？<br />\n<br />\n加埋取消美港政策法，為左保命，契弟走得麽，會將絕大部份資金兌美金射走去外國，小心駛得萬年船！手足自行決定啦！"},{"pid":"606ff8fdd9d47fb9d8ea171ba75b934d9dd7fc61","tid":2045430,"uid":193100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T21:13:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1587732513627&amp;issue=20200424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1587732513627%26issue%3D20200424&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=7924c9c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1587732513627%26issue%3D20200424&h=5f1344a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1587732513627&amp;issue=20200424</a><br />\n所謂的DCEP即是Digital Currency Electronic Payment，是由中國人民銀行發行、具有價值特徵及流通現金（M0）屬性的數碼支付工具。由於人行發行的DCEP，DCEP與人民幣有相同法定地位，相當於電子版人民幣，除了具有法律補償性外，規定任何中國機構及14億人民不能拒絕DCEP。<br />\n目前DCEP正在上述4個城市進行內部測試，特別是透過DCEP發放補貼金，未來DCEP甚至可以直接發放工資、個人貸款又或者特定的現金。雖說人行沒有限制DCEP以那一種技術進行兌換，商業機構/銀行可以利用區塊鏈技術、透過傳統帳戶又或是電子支付工具如支付寶等，人行均不會干涉。不過大家要清楚明白，無論用那一種技術兌換DCEP，中央今後對每一分一毫電子貨幣的走向均瞭若指掌。"},{"pid":"07d2e7eb9c422e4c9909c612702bde3429324c5a","tid":2045430,"uid":193100,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T21:14:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dbs.com.hk/corporate-zh/aics/templatedata/article/generic/data/zh/CIO/092019/190911-asia_hk.xml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dbs.com.hk%2Fcorporate-zh%2Faics%2Ftemplatedata%2Farticle%2Fgeneric%2Fdata%2Fzh%2FCIO%2F092019%2F190911-asia_hk.xml&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=9eddefc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dbs.com.hk/corporate-zh/aics/templatedata/article/generic/data/zh/CIO/092019/190911-asia_hk.xml</a><br />\n中國急於製造自己的電子貨幣<br />\n<br />\n人民銀行可能使用電子貨幣來引導經濟"},{"pid":"b56186d628558d792a76713f3d56a199e3152781","tid":2045430,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T22:47:11.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"819766d4dd816f65c54678689b95dab5752d86a6","tid":2045430,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:00:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49c4d3a77f53bcec9249111d46a5dd02ae3e788c","tid":2045430,"uid":186431,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:08:04.000Z","msg":"啱啱換晒人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e9c9edfe5d93b1990a221ff315ff47cdb074e7","tid":2045430,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07d2e7eb9c422e4c9909c612702bde3429324c5a","tid":2045430,"uid":193100,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T21:14:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dbs.com.hk/corporate-zh/aics/templatedata/article/generic/data/zh/CIO/092019/190911-asia_hk.xml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dbs.com.hk%2Fcorporate-zh%2Faics%2Ftemplatedata%2Farticle%2Fgeneric%2Fdata%2Fzh%2FCIO%2F092019%2F190911-asia_hk.xml&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8